ime":"2018-03-12T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dfde8c2c6fd59c079289ab320321d3147d0c088","tid":586811,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd1db1fa0ac45180eccf91db2ebbcb31f47ffd6","tid":586811,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png&h=6c9baf49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多撚謝販民班大愛支（尤其民主党工党同社民狗！）囉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟德一早都知係港共專登設計既市區票倉膽！！！！</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n「姚松炎今次做選舉工程，同我哋傳統政黨，真係好唔同，我哋唔係好慣，尤其係打開地面戰嗰班，其實一直覺得佢危。<br />\n<br />\n我哋擺街站、洗樓、去屋邨，佢哋認為唔使做好多呢啲，覺得做好網上，網上反應熱烈，就好有信心。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d840a03af89c470ceef496df55adc778728b863f","tid":586811,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:08:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5431f9e086aced8b3b1a9fca77baeb31ebc39c99","tid":586811,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"push"}]}